Hello everyone,
Here I am making this post because since July 1st I have had a bad trip on LSD,
I want to say that before this bad trip I would hit 20 nails a day and I would do some 1 w.k every two months with big Defonce (Taz, coke, LSD, and all the rest)...For 3 years,
now I will tell you how it goes.
a Good w.k is waiting for me
on Friday evening everything goes well
one has to consume 5 grams of speed plus all the MD,
Saturday morning after a sleepless night I go to work just in the morning from 9am to 12pm in the afternoon,
we continued,
I continued on my side to tap bullets and to tap speed,
a colleague is holding the glass with a drop of the LSD vial for me
I hesitated at the beginning then after I told myself let me take it (something I should not have done).
the evening continued normally and the other two so-called colleagues had decided to make us have a great time with the colleagues.....
on this famous beach there were people and one of the two colleagues said there is no one looking for shit we are going to beat them ...
I said to myself that the product had to come down because I couldn't fight like that
so I forced myself to resist the product,
the ,the paranoia begins to invade me all while making a mise en scene
the two other colleague who had not taken anything, began to look for the guys who were angry with us
me being totally confused I told myself it will leave at any moment,
Time passes, nothing happens.
well we leave the beach and go to my place,
I ask them if the guys are following us,
he does not reply,
we arrive at my place and there he leaves me all alone at home with my girlfriend who was sleeping...,
I keep on doing bad all night
I can't sleep, I think and at the slightest noise I go out with a bat....
the days this rises and I begin to fall asleep because I just realized that there was nothing,
the night passes normally ,
I get up and I am still under the effect of LSD and the rest.
I said to myself it's normal
so it was Sunday and the next day I had to work.
the day is going normally
I type some screw then I nap ,
Sunday passes and Monday arrives
I still feel like a mess,
I still think it's normal with the box I took....
so at 2 pm I had to take the job
I eat a little and I take a big dose of speed to get high...
so I take the car and I go to taff
get to the taff ,as soon as I open the store I start to get dizzy my heart starts to beat at 200 and I feel that I am going to have a fainting spell ,
by reassuring me I will buy some Snickers bars and something to drink,
after that I go back to the taff and another crisis...
panicked I called my mother.. because the colleague was not the one...
after his mother took me to the doctor
he asks me what I did and then I unpack all my bag
and my mother rather took it well in the end she knew that I was crooked..
The Doctor tells me to wait for the product to come down, it will take a few months, then that's it,
I told her that I had trouble seeing.
I told her that I had trouble seeing.
he told me that it was normal too and that he was going to go down,
for my anxiety attacks he prescribed lizanxia an anti axiolitite finally against anxiety ,
I take 1 in the morning and 1 in the evening.
it calms me down but the voices in my head don't stop,
it often gives me a headache...
after this Bad I have stopped all more wax more nothing,
my girlfriend does not understand what happened to me and does not care
